DejaView — provenance and third-party attributions
===================================================

DejaView decodes the DjVu image format, which is openly published. The decoder
is built from public and permissively-licensed sources.

ZP arithmetic coder, JB2, IW44 wavelet, BZZ
-------------------------------------------
These codecs implement the public DjVu format. They were cross-referenced
against DjvuNet (https://github.com/DjvuNet/DjvuNet), an MIT-licensed .NET DjVu
library. The ZP coder adaptation table (src/zp_table.js) is taken from DjvuNet.
